祝福的人生是分享的人生，给与的人生。\r\n\r\n祝大家幸福！\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Blessed Life', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '176-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-12-13 15:58:35', '2013-12-13 07:58:35', '', 176, 'http://qdgytrans.com/wordpress/?p=178', 0, 'revision', '', 0)#endQuery
