INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (ID, post_author, post_date, post_date_gmt, post_content, post_title, post_excerpt, post_status, comment_status, ping_status, post_password, post_name, to_ping, pinged, post_modified, post_modified_gmt, post_content_filtered, post_parent, guid, menu_order, post_type, post_mime_type, comment_count) VALUES (262, 1, '2014-02-03 19:10:59', '2014-02-03 11:10:59', '<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/The-Blessed-Life-Achieving-Guaranteed/dp/0830736352\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\" wp-image-177    alignleft\" title=\"The Blessed Life\" alt=\"blessed-life\" src=\"http://qdgytrans.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/blessed-life-203x300.jpg\" width=\"122\" height=\"180\" /></a>最近认识了一个非常聪明，善解人意的女孩。每次认识新朋友的时候总有一种说不出的喜悦。她最喜欢的一本书是 \"The Blessed Life\".\r\n在她的推荐下，我开始每天晚上开始读这本书，我被这本书迷住了。\r\n\r\n这本书不一定适合所有的人，但是如果你觉得这个社会压你压得很累，需要换个角度思考的时候，请务必看一下这本书。\r\n\r\n这本书涉及很多基督教的内容，如果你不是基督徒也也不要一下否决。我从这本书里摘取了一句短文不会让你觉得太宗教化。\r\n\r\nWhen you give away an apple seed by planting it, you don\'t just get back an apple seed. In time, you actually get back a whole apple tree, and on that tree are many apples, and on that tree are many apples, and each apple has many seeds. You get back so much more than you actually give.\r\n\r\n如果我们把世间的财富，名声，权力等都归结到自己身上。想尽办法去争取的话，我们的心只会越活很累，得不到一丝安宁。但是如果我们把这些世俗的东西看轻了，愿意分享自己已拥有的东西，那些我们原本拼命追求的东西自然而然就已在我们的身边了。\r\n\r\n被祝福的人生是分享的人生，给与的人生。\r\n\r\n<strong>祝大家幸福！</strong>', 'The Blessed Life', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '176-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-03 19:10:59', '2014-02-03 11:10:59', '', 176, 'http://qdgytrans.com/wordpress/2014/02/03/176-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0)#endQuery
